{"tid":309583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警葵涌工廈內燒炭亡　妻召鎖匠開門揭發","createTime":"2017-07-05T06:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T14:16:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9fa7648233601af26695301b7b1929df72a891d","tid":309583,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T06:54:02.000Z","msg":"上午11時14分，警方接報一名男子在葵涌華星街保盈工業大廈一單位內燒炭自殺。救護員到場經檢驗，證實該名男子已告身亡。警方調查後，初步相信死者是一名警務人員，隸屬新界南交通部。今早死者妻子到來找尋，並召鎖匠開門揭發事件。"},{"pid":"42be71fd33068aacbf34e77d20f767047755d7ab","tid":309583,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56916000&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170705\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56916000%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170705&d=ZETiPhJ0t%2B%2BGroWVQ6EUKZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7e2a93ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56916000%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170705&h=c8a644b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56916000&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170705</a>"},{"pid":"c319083431b4d86c2c963fff8be932b9ca744a60","tid":309583,"uid":122,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:13:02.000Z","msg":"阿sir 燒炭唔使你教"},{"pid":"b4b4e9ff6a3321dc3304878beffc963febc6a85d","tid":309583,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d74f08d3b50193335d78b19dee8eea0a7405d9","tid":309583,"uid":44333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:41:40.000Z","msg":"又死一件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8abb8435a11901e8be9bb13c3d99fe4515c13d7","tid":309583,"uid":21121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:44:26.000Z","msg":"一個女人無左個好老公<br />\n快d衝出來捐錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e5517c29140a0678c4a1d614c71b55211faefa","tid":309583,"uid":38740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:45:19.000Z","msg":"租工廈"},{"pid":"d72673b02e03c1a45c0f845628cab715d24f2f17","tid":309583,"uid":522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/ftp/News/20141018/HK/_18GK004_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FTor%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20141018%2FHK%2F_18GK004_.jpg&h=56bfab67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfcd60f3208b04b319029016412579100e96e416","tid":309583,"uid":48246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:51:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/ftp/News/20141018/HK/_18GK004_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FTor%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20141018%2FHK%2F_18GK004_.jpg&h=56bfab67&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n共業。"},{"pid":"ea9c81f2316e37e6c45fbe9e0691c1c0158d47ea","tid":309583,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"交通部都要燒？"},{"pid":"d22312af71e9bef285c4d9e38e682633f17649e0","tid":309583,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:57:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>交通部都要燒？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似話係偷左隻勞個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 呀sir燒炭唔洗你教"},{"pid":"bf9648ddb129eecc6dc40e850816171297716998","tid":309583,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:16:16.000Z","msg":"葵涌華星街保盈工業大廈，上午11時14分，一名女子報案，指其丈夫於單位內燒炭昏迷。救護員到場經檢驗，證實該名男子已告身亡。警方調查後，證實死者姓伍(39歲)是警務人員，隸屬新界南交通部。據悉，他是早前的警嫂炒勞案中其中一名受害人。<br />\n<br />\n警隊3年前爆出「炒賣兵團」醜聞，一名警員與妻子涉訛稱可以半價買Chanel貨品，又稱炒賣名牌手錶及手袋可大賺，叫人集資加入並將收益歸事主，兩年間有多達14人加入，當中包括警員。據悉，死者是案中其中一名受害人。"},{"pid":"18560c1dff6f768d230a324745592ba3623d71f0","tid":309583,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:19:33.000Z","msg":"死得好<br />\n黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6f70f304aaf98a1235bdeb4783a6ccb940693e","tid":309583,"uid":7323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:28:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">死得好</span>"},{"pid":"5be3fa49050c0d83481a30eab708ac6afd9e71fc","tid":309583,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:33:36.000Z","msg":"呀sir都要租工廈單位住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd87a124ebc203e62e61ab5ba07ae32f3077eab5","tid":309583,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T10:39:27.000Z","msg":"想保住退体金？"},{"pid":"71d01bbfe8c01f1872565cce8bd0db21ce7554ee","tid":309583,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T11:16:12.000Z","msg":"交通警工廈劏房燒炭亡。現場是華星街16-18號保盈工業大廈4樓，上址有3000多呎，被間成12間劏房單位，每間約百多呎，上午11時許，一名姓伍男子（39歲）在其中一個劏房單位內燒炭，一名男住客發現報警，警員和救護員接報趕至，發現伍倒臥床邊，毫無反應，檢查後證實已死亡。警方封鎖現場調查，死者遺物中包括有紅酒。 <br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，上址的單位最近被租用作聯誼活動，死者為警員，隸屬新界南總區交通部特別調查隊，與妻育有一子(8歲)一女(6歲)，伍疑因婚姻問題，獨自搬到上址劏房居住，昨晚（7月4日）曾與太太聯絡，並沒有留下遺書。警方獲悉後大為緊張，將案件交由葵青區重案組跟進，並通知新界南交通部警員到場了解。死者妻子曾到場了解，並通知開鎖匠為警方開門。"},{"pid":"1b1322c4186a4a524c6b8ad1b4c6f4b474e40142","tid":309583,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T12:02:04.000Z","msg":"遲下屙唔出屎都要自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d07556c8fac8638c514e4c4ff062e93bb752e6","tid":309583,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc5c1e3dd56637c5e89041439a289457dae7ec55","tid":309583,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T12:15:09.000Z","msg":"個女人係咪要交返宿舍岀黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b40ce5ce47228b9b0515a23c232a6d0d9671ebe","tid":309583,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:16:43.000Z","msg":"天有光如來佛祖夥我靠岸"}]}